name: Handmade Hessian Coffee Sack Cushion
description:
These cushions have been handmade here by the Lot No.32 team here in the UK using authentic Coffee Sacks. 
 
Due to the nature of hessian being a natural product, slight imperfections and shade difference may occur. You will receive a unique cushion, designs will vary. If you have a particular request on design from the pictures shown then please confirm this on your order. 
 
Spot Clean Only.

Price is per cushion. 

Dimensions: 50cm x 50cm (20 x 20")  
Filling made from: Polyester fibres. 


Please note cushion inner cannot be removed.

name: Vintage Leather Chesterfield Sofa
description:
Beautifully worn Vintage Leather Chesterfield Sofa. 

Hessian lined bottom does require replacing and there is a small tear to the seating cushion you will see in picture. Plenty of character for this beautiful sofa.
